+{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_019dMinMkZdUGHhpYGesbozK","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"OK so `connectWs` + `waitForMessage` is the issue. But debug3 which does the same thing inline works. Let me check what's different more carefully.\n\nIn debug3:\n```js\nconst ws = new WebSocket(url);\nconst msg = await new Promise((resolve, reject) => {\n  const timer = setTimeout(() => reject(new Error(\"Timeout\")), 5000);\n  ws.on(\"open\", () => { });\n  ws.on(\"message\", (data) => { clearTimeout(timer); resolve(data.toString()); });\n  ws.on(\"error\", (err) => { clearTimeout(timer); reject(err); });\n});\n```\n\nIn debug5:\n```js\n// connectWs: resolves on 'open', THEN\n// waitForMessage: listens for 'message'\nconst ws = await connectWs(doc.id);  // waits for 'open'\nconst msg = await waitForMessage(ws); // THEN waits for 'message'\n```\n\nThe difference is: in debug3, the `message` listener is registered BEFORE the socket opens. In debug5 (`connectWs`), we first wait for `open`, and then register the `message` listener. The `sync` message is sent in the `handleConnection` callback which runs when the WebSocket is established. The message might be sent during the `handleUpgrade` callback, which fires before the client's `open` event. So by the time `open` fires and we call `waitForMessage`, the `message` event has already been emitted and missed.\n\nThat's the race condition! The server sends the `sync` message immediately in `handleConnection`, which is called from the `handleUpgrade` callback. The `message` event on the client fires before the `open` event (or right at the same time). By the time `connectWs` resolves and we call `waitForMessage`, the message was already emitted.\n\nThe fix: register the `message` listener BEFORE the `open` event, or better yet, use a helper that collects all messages from the start.\n\nLet me fix the `connectWs` to also capture the first message, or change the approach to set up message listener immediately."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":502,"cache_read_input_tokens":81147,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":502},"output_tokens":2,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"889fa0f9-7abc-4e52-9e88-0ef573ab4c1d","uuid":"8c8e2ba7-5dd8-448f-8943-73cd60ef0a5e"}
